oys where it is found that the calculated equilibrium\ncross-sections are in a good agreement with observations from selected alloys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 May 2016 00:05:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 May 2016 15:25:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-13"}
